Technical task
  - create a new angular project
  - remove the default data that comes with the new project (from the .html, .css file)
  - add a new component called header. Add the title of the app to this component
  - commit the changes and publish them in a repository on Github
  
Second set of technical tasks:
  - we need a new component to hold the main content of the page. Please create a new component called "main-content"
  - we also need a footer. This will be similar to the header component, but will be located at the buttom of the page.
  
